G-1145,
E-Notification of Application/Petition Acceptance
Use this form to request a text message and/or email when USCIS accepts your form.
Forms and Document Downloads
Form G-1145
(PDF, 245.09 KB)
Form Details
Edition Date
09/26/14
.
You can also use previous editions. You can find the edition date at the bottom of the page.
Dates are listed in mm/dd/yy format.
If you complete and print this form to mail it, make sure that the form edition date and page numbers are visible at the bottom of all pages and that all pages are from the same form edition. If any of the form’s pages are missing or are from a different form edition, we may reject your form.
If you need help downloading and printing forms, read our
instructions
.
Where to File
Clip the completed Form G-1145 to the front of the application or petition you are filing.
You may submit Form G-1145 with the following forms:
EOIR-29, Notice of Appeal to the Board of Immigration Appeals from a Decision of a DHS Officer;
I-102, Application for Replacement/Initial Nonimmigrant Arrival-Departure Document;
I-130, Petition for Alien Relative;
I-131, Application for Travel Documents, Parole Documents, and Arrival-Departure Documents;
I-140, Immigrant Petition for Alien Worker;
I-212, Application for Permission to Reapply for Admission into the U.S. After Deportation or Removal;
I-360, Petition for Amerasian, Widow(er) or Special Immigrant;
I-485, Application to Register Permanent Residence or Adjust Status;
I-485 Supp A, Supplement A to Form I-485, Adjustment of Status Under Section 245(i);
I-589, Application for Asylum and for Withholding of Removal;
I-601, Application for Waiver of Grounds of Inadmissibility;
I-601A, Application for Provisional Unlawful Presence Waiver;
I-694, Notice of Appeal of Decision Under Sections 245A or 210 of the Immigration and Nationality Act;
I-698, Application to Adjust Status from Temporary to Permanent Resident (Under Section 245A of the INA);
I-765, Application for Employment Authorization;
I-800, Petition to Classify Convention Adoptee as an Immediate Relative;
I-800A, Application for Determination of Suitability to Adopt a Child from a Convention Country;
I-817, Application for Family Unity Benefits;
I-821, Application for Temporary Protected Status;
I-821D, Consideration of Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals;
I-824, Application for Action on an Approved Application or Petition;
N-565, Application for Replacement Naturalization/Citizenship Document; or
N-600K, Application for Citizenship and Issuance of Certificate under Section 322.
Filing Fee
You can find the filing fee for Form G-1145 by visiting our
Fee Schedule
page.
Special Instructions
This service is only available for certain forms filed at our four Lockbox locations in Lewisville, Texas; Chicago, Illinois; Elgin, Illinois; and Phoenix, Arizona.
E-Notifications do not include any personal information, including your name, because email and text message are not secure ways for us to transmit this information.  The notification will list your receipt number and tell you how to obtain case status information.
